China Motor Denies Report of a $1 Billion South African Factory Investment

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-22T06:27:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/china-motor-denies-report-of-a-1-billion-south-african-factory-investment.html
China Motor Corp. (2204)  has no plans to
build a factory in  South Africa , company spokeswoman Anny Fu
said by telephone today.  The Johannesburg-based Business Day newspaper reported June
21 that China Motor plans to build a $1 billion factory near
Harrismith in South Africa.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chua Kong Ho at 
 kchua6@bloomberg.net  